title: HAMRADIO : A52A Bhutan 2000
description:
The Secret Kingdom of the Himalayas

Tucked away, far up in the Eastern Himalayas is the tiny Kingdom of Bhutan - one of the most isolated and unknown nations on Earth - and one of the most wanted DXCC entities of all time.

This film will take you to a nation and a people rarely seen by the outside world (even on television or video). Experience what is actually like to be behind the scenes at one of the world&#039;s ultimate destinations with some of the best operators ever assembled.
